
Privacy Policy for Crop Clinic
Introduction
Welcome to Crop Clinic! Your privacy is of paramount importance to us. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your information when you use our application for crop monitoring. By using Crop Clinic, you agree to the terms and conditions of this Privacy Policy.

Information We Collect
Personal Information
We may collect the following personal information from you:

Name
Contact Information (email address, phone number)
Location Data
User ID and Password
Any other information you provide directly to us through the app
Non-Personal Information
We may collect non-personal information about your use of the app, such as:

Device Information (e.g., device type, operating system)
Usage Data (e.g., pages visited, time spent on the app)
IP Address
How We Use Your Information
We use the information we collect for the following purposes:

To provide and maintain our services
To improve and personalize the user experience
To communicate with you about updates, promotions, and news related to Crop Clinic
To respond to your inquiries and provide customer support
To analyze usage patterns and improve the functionality of the app
To comply with legal obligations
Sharing Your Information
We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to outside parties except as described below:

With your consent
To trusted third parties who assist us in operating our app and conducting our business, provided they agree to keep your information confidential
To comply with legal requirements, enforce our policies, or protect our rights and the rights of others
Data Security
We implement a variety of security measures to ensure the safety of your personal information. However, please be aware that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

Your Choices
You have the right to:

Access, correct, or delete your personal information
Opt-out of receiving marketing communications from us
Disable location tracking through your device settings
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

Email: simple2manage@gmail.com
Address: 2nd floor, Administrative Block, Kerala Startup Mission, Palakkad, Kerala - 678007, India
By using Crop Clinic, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy and agree to be bound by its terms and conditions.

Last updated: 26/06/2024

This Privacy Policy is designed to comply with the relevant privacy laws in India. Please ensure you review and adjust it as necessary to fit your specific requirements and legal obligations.
